LanguageData.CWAS.aaWarning:
Alpha Animals is also active. That mod has settings for defining the spawn-rate of the animals in it but it works by adding a multiplier to the value instead of changing it.
The values you will see in this mods settings are the actual spawn-values. Any changes done in Alpa Animals will still be applied in game, they will just not be shown in the settings of this mod.
To keep it simple I suggest you just use this mods settings for modifying the spawn rate and leave the multiplier in Alpha Animals at 1x.
